{"cacheTime": 1595524027, "baseUrl": "https://kater.me/d/82146", "title": "《巨神與誓女》日本推出時間公開，收集故事線索開創玩家專屬劇情", "content": [{"author": "Soro", "body": "\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/mGWC2IO.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mGWC2IO.jpg\" title=\"\"/>\n</a>\n<br/>\n 日本 Exnoa 預定於手機與 PC 等平台上推出的網頁新作幻想 RPG《巨神與誓女》（巨神と誓女），宣布將決定於 2020 年 7 月 21 日正式展開營運服務。\n </p>\n<p>\n 《巨神與誓女》為一款以既沒有白天，也沒有黑夜，永恆持續著黃昏的幻想世界作為舞台，讓玩家們與不知從何而來的「巨神」展開無止盡對抗的幻想 RPG 遊戲。而且遊戲中最特別的一點，就是玩家們並不是順著故事劇情來推進遊戲進度，而是必須收集遊戲內散落各處的線索，來自行推測劇情，藉此不斷創造衍生故事發展！\n <br/>\n<span data-s9e-mediaembed=\"youtube\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:100%;max-width:640px\">\n<span style=\"display:block;overflow:hidden;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%\">\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/pSyzqkDNXNc\" style=\"background:url(https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pSyzqkDNXNc/hqdefault.jpg) 50% 50% / cover;border:0;height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;width:100%\">\n</iframe>\n</span>\n</span>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/N82fOe1.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/N82fOe1.jpg\" title=\"\"/>\n</a>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/PfP9f4u.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PfP9f4u.jpg\" title=\"\"/>\n</a>\n<br/>\n 官網\n <br/>\n<a href=\"https://www.dmm.com/netgame/feature/kyoshintoseijyo.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n https://www.dmm.com/netgame/feature/kyoshintoseijyo.html\n </a>\n</p>\n"}, {"author": "姆蜜一雙藍黑狂暴巨雙炫劍擬招重砍一夏天仲玉模式", "body": "\n<p>\n 聽起來好累\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "Soro", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"835444\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/82146/2\">\n 姆蜜一雙藍黑狂暴巨雙炫劍擬招重砍一夏天仲玉模式\n </a>\n 加上是日文…\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "姆蜜一雙藍黑狂暴巨雙炫劍擬招重砍一夏天仲玉模式", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"835452\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/82146/3\">\n Soro\n </a>\n 日文pass…\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "∅nu", "body": "\n<p>\n 回合制….\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "Fruit丨vinegar", "body": "\n<p>\n dmm 都很老套\n </p>\n"}]}